            <h2>How RequireHire's AI Voice Mock Interviews Build Confidence Step-by-Step</h2>
            
            <h3>1. Speak Naturally — No Judgment, Just Practice</h3>
            <p>The AI interviewer feels real. You speak in English or Hindi, answer common questions (technical, behavioral, HR), and the system listens like a human. No awkward silence from a friend who doesn't know what to ask.</p>

            <h3>2. Instant, Honest Feedback That Guides Improvement</h3>
            <p>After each session you get detailed scores and tips on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Clarity & pace of speech</li>
                <li>Confidence level (detected via tone & filler words)</li>
                <li>Relevance & structure of answers</li>
                <li>Technical accuracy (for role-specific questions)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This feedback loop is powerful — you see progress after just 3–5 sessions, which builds momentum and self-belief.</p>

<grok-card data-id="62ca37" data-type="image_card" data-plain-type="render_searched_image"  data-arg-size="LARGE" ></grok-card>


