            <h3>4. Skill Score Visibility — Proof of Progress</h3>
            <p>Your AI-generated skill score rises as you improve. Seeing the number climb (e.g., from 62 → 88) gives tangible proof that you're getting better — massive for confidence, especially for freshers who feel "not good enough."</p>

            <h3>5. Real-World Transfer: From Mock to Actual Interviews</h3>
            <p>Regular practice reduces freeze-ups, helps structure answers (STAR method naturally improves), and makes you comfortable thinking on your feet. Many RequireHire users report cracking interviews they previously failed due to nerves.</p>

